Table oms.ProcessesDO

List of business processes of the IOM.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
asyncProcessing boolean Whether the process is allowed to run asynchronously. 
syncProcessing boolean Whether the process is allowed to run synchronously. 
description varchar(200) Description of the process. 
timeToLive bigint Duration in milliseconds that a JMS-message is valid for this process. If NULL, there is no limit. 
ProcessDefDO processDefRef integer UNIQUE, NOT_NULL The process of the process definition that will be extended.
